issue.title: gapi.auth2 and Chrome Extension Incompatibility
issue.body:
Looks gapi.auth2 does not [support](https://github.com/google/google-api-javascript-client/issues/312) Chrome Extensions. 

Alternatives include: Chrome.identity and Firebase Auth.

Some resources for Chrome.Identity: 
[Chrome Identity API](https://developer.chrome.com/apps/identity)
[Example app](https://github.com/GoogleChrome/chrome-app-samples/tree/master/samples/identity)

If anyone can incorporate Chrome.Identity, that would make the application functional as a Chrome Extension.
